# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#1248, the recommended behavior is to not commit Pipfile.lock
#   when you are developing an app (as opposed to a library).
# Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similarly, poetry.lock is usually committed, but can be ignored if desired.
# poetry.lock

# pdm
#   Similarly, pdm.lock is usually committed, but can be ignored if desired.
